---
title: Pork Chops and Mushroom-Sour Cream Sauce with Roasted Green Beans
description: This mushroom-sour cream sauce, rich in umami and tangy flavours, will be your new classic favourite. Mashed potatoes with velvety mushrooms and tender roasted green beans offer lovely textures to this stick-to-your-ribs dinner with minimal fuss!
